Eroarea:   SELECT {2} AS "IdAuto", X.* FROM (

                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) AS int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                                LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                                LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607
                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = {0}
                                UNION
                                SELECT B.F10003 AS F10003, A.F10008 {1} ' ' {1} a.F10009 AS "NumeComplet", A.F10008 AS "Nume", A.F10009 AS "Prenume", 
                                A.F10017 AS "CNP", A.F10022 AS "DataAngajarii",A.F10011 AS "NrContract", E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", 
                                G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Departament", D.F71804 AS "Functia", 
                                CAST(COALESCE(A.F10043,0) as int) AS "Norma", A.F100901, A.F10022, A.F10023, COALESCE(C."IdRol",1) AS "IdRol", COALESCE(A.F10025,0) AS F10025
                                FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_relGrupSuper" C ON b."IdGrup" = c."IdGrup"
                                INNER JOIN F100 A ON b.F10003 = a.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802

                                CASE WHEN ("Mail" IS NULL OR LEN("Mail") = 0) THEN F100894 ELSE "Mail" END AS "Email",
                                CASE WHEN (F100894 IS NULL OR LEN(F100894) = 0) AND ("Mail" IS NULL OR LEN("Mail") = 0) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "AreMail",

                                 ,CTG."Denumire" AS "Categorie"

                                INNER JOIN F1001 X ON A.F10003 = X.F10003                            
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802                                
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202

                                WHERE C."IdSuper" = 2 

                                UNION

                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper")

Eroarea:   BEGIN
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F1 = (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(ValStr,'') = 'CO' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)    FROM Ptj_Intrari   WHERE year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F2 = (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(ValStr,'') = 'CM' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)    FROM Ptj_Intrari   WHERE year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F3 = (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(ValStr,'') = 'EV' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)    FROM Ptj_Intrari   WHERE year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F4 = (SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN COALESCE(ValStr,'') = 'CFP' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)    FROM Ptj_Intrari   WHERE year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

UPDATE ent

                            SET ent.F14 = (select isnull(F1,0) +isnull(F2,0) + isnull(F3,0)+isnull(F4,0) + isnull(F9,0) +isnull(F8,0) + isnull(F13,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat 
  where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F16 = (select isnull(F5,0) * isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003   where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

select isnull(F12,0)*2 + isnull(F11,0) from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

                            SET ent.F15 = (select (isnull(F30,0) - isnull(F14,0))* isnull(F100.f100973,0) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F18 = (select (case when 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0)>0 then 2*isnull(f12,0)-isnull(f5,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F19 = (select isnull(F5,0) - ((isnull(F12,0)*2) - isnull(F18,0)/F100.F100973) from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

                            SET ent.F20 = (select (case when isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0)>0 then isnull(f11,0)-isnull(f19,0) else 0 end)*F100.F100973 
from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=ent.F10003 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

END;

                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=ent.F10003 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

END;

 from  ptj_cumulat

                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent

from Ptj_Cumulat inner join f100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003  
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003)

                            SET ent.F21 = (Select isnull(F10,0)+isnull(F20,0) from Ptj_Cumulat where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F22 = (Select (isnull(F5,0)-isnull(F19,0))/2 from Ptj_Cumulat 
where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F23 = ( SELECT Ramase FROM SituatieZileAbsente WHERE F10003=ent.F10003 AND An=YEAR(ent.DataInceput)) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F43 = (select   f30 - cast (case when isnull(F100.F10043,0)=0 then  isnull(F15,0)/8  else   isnull(F11,0) /F100.F10043 end as int) - isnull(F1,0) - isnull(F2,0) - isnull(F3,0)
- isnull(F4,0)
- isnull(F6,0)
 from  ptj_cumulat inner join F100 on ptj_cumulat.F10003 = F100.F10003 
  where an=ent.An and Luna=ent.Luna and ptj_cumulat.F10003 = ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;
UPDATE ent 
                            SET ent.F30 = (select sum (case when  zilibera >0 or  ZiLiberaLegala > 0  then 0 else 1 end) from ptj_intrari
join f100 on ptj_intrari.f10003 = f100.f10003 and cast(ziua as date) between f10022 and f10023
 where year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE ent.F10003 IN (9) AND 202009 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202009;

END;

                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN '#ffff8000' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN '#dc96dc' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= cast(getdate() as date)  AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= F100923 AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= F100924) THEN '#ffffffc8' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= cast(getdate() as date)  AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= A.F100916) THEN '#FF0066FF' ELSE '#ffc8ffc8' END END) ELSE '#ffffc8c8' END) END END AS "Culoare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 900 THEN 'Candidat' ELSE CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 999 THEN 'Angajat in avans' ELSE (CASE WHEN A.F10025 = 0 THEN (CASE WHEN (A.F100925 <> 0 AND F100922 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100923 IS NOT NULL AND F100922 <= cast(getdate() as date)  AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= F100923 AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= F100924) THEN 'Activ suspendat' ELSE CASE WHEN (A.F100915 <= cast(getdate() as date)  AND cast(getdate() as date)  <= A.F100916) THEN 'Activ detasat' ELSE 'Activ' END END) ELSE 'Inactiv' END) END END AS "Stare",
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10083,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE CASE WHEN adr."IdTipStrada" IN NULL OR adr."IdTipStrada" = 0 THEN ' Str. ' ELSE (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "tblTipStrada" WHERE "Id" = adr."IdTipStrada") + ' ' END + a.F10083 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10084,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Nr. ' + a.F10084 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10085,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Bloc. ' + a.F10085 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100892,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Sc. ' + a.F100892 END) +
                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F100893,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Et. ' + a.F100893 END) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100897 is null or a.F100897 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when niv3.tip in (11, 19, 22, 23) then ' sat ' + niv3.denloc else
                            case when niv3.tip = 6 and upper(niv3.denloc) not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' + niv3.DENLOC else ' ' + niv3.denloc end END end) +

                            (case when a.F100914 is null or a.F100914 = 0 THEN '' else case when niv2.tip in (1, 4) and UPPER(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + niv2.DENLOC else

                            case when niv2.TIP = 3 and upper(niv2.DENLOC) not like '%COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' + niv2.DENLOC else ' ' + niv2.denloc end end end end ) +

                            (CASE WHEN a.F100921 is null or a.F100921 = 0 THEN '' ELSE case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%JUDET%' or upper(niv1.denloc)  like '%MUNICIPIU%' then ' ' + niv1.DENLOC else
                             case when upper(niv1.denloc) like '%BUCURESTI%' then ' municipiul ' + niv1.DENLOC else ' judetul ' + niv1.denloc end end END) +
                            

                            (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A.F10087,'') = '' THEN '' ELSE ' Cod Postal. ' + a.F10087 END) AS "AdresaCompleta"
                             
                            FROM F100 A
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202 
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304 
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405 
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506 
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607 
                            left join Localitati niv1 on niv1.SIRUTA = a.F100921
                            left join Localitati niv2 on niv2.SIRUTA = a.F100914
                            left join Localitati niv3 on niv3.SIRUTA = a.F100897
                            LEFT JOIN "F100Adrese" adr ON adr.F10003 = a.F10003
                             
                            WHERE 1=1 AND adr."Principal" =1  AND A.F10003 IN (SELECT CAST(F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM USERS WHERE F70102 = 2
                            UNION
                            SELECT B.F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE C."IdSuper" = 2  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 )
                            UNION
                            SELECT CAST(B.F10003 AS INT) AS F10003 FROM "relGrupAngajat" B
                            INNER JOIN "MP_relGrupSuper" C ON B."IdGrup" = C."IdGrup"
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" D ON B.F10003=D.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = -1 * D."IdSuper"
                             inner join f100 e on b.F10003=e.F10003 
                            WHERE D."IdUser" = 2  AND ( e.F10025 = 0  OR  e.F10025 = 999 ))
                            ) X WHERE 1=1  AND ( "Stare"='Activ' OR  "Stare"='Angajat in avans')
                            ORDER BY "NumeComplet"

                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-10-01], [2019-10-02], [2019-10-03], [2019-10-04], [2019-10-05], [2019-10-06], [2019-10-07], [2019-10-08], [2019-10-09], [2019-10-10], [2019-10-11], [2019-10-12], [2019-10-13], [2019-10-14], [2019-10-15], [2019-10-16], [2019-10-17], [2019-10-18], [2019-10-19], [2019-10-20], [2019-10-21], [2019-10-22], [2019-10-23], [2019-10-24], [2019-10-25], [2019-10-26], [2019-10-27], [2019-10-28], [2019-10-29], [2019-10-30], [2019-10-31] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 10 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003

                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract

                                SELECT *,

                                INNER JOIN tblZile Y ON '2019-06-01' <= Y.Zi AND Y.Zi <= '2019-06-30'

                                FROM Ptj_Cumulat X 
		                        LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStari st on st.Id = x.IdStare
		                        left join SituatieZileAbsente zabs on zabs.F10003 = x.F10003 and zabs.An = x.An and zabs.IdAbsenta = (select Id from Ptj_tblAbsente where DenumireScurta = 'CO')
		                        left join SituatieZLP zlp on zlp.F10003 = x.F10003 and zlp.An = x.An
                                INNER JOIN (SELECT F10003 , [2019-06-01] AS "Ziua1", [2019-06-02] AS "Ziua2", [2019-06-03] AS "Ziua3", [2019-06-04] AS "Ziua4", [2019-06-05] AS "Ziua5", [2019-06-06] AS "Ziua6", [2019-06-07] AS "Ziua7", [2019-06-08] AS "Ziua8", [2019-06-09] AS "Ziua9", [2019-06-10] AS "Ziua10", [2019-06-11] AS "Ziua11", [2019-06-12] AS "Ziua12", [2019-06-13] AS "Ziua13", [2019-06-14] AS "Ziua14", [2019-06-15] AS "Ziua15", [2019-06-16] AS "Ziua16", [2019-06-17] AS "Ziua17", [2019-06-18] AS "Ziua18", [2019-06-19] AS "Ziua19", [2019-06-20] AS "Ziua20", [2019-06-21] AS "Ziua21", [2019-06-22] AS "Ziua22", [2019-06-23] AS "Ziua23", [2019-06-24] AS "Ziua24", [2019-06-25] AS "Ziua25", [2019-06-26] AS "Ziua26", [2019-06-27] AS "Ziua27", [2019-06-28] AS "Ziua28", [2019-06-29] AS "Ziua29", [2019-06-30] AS "Ziua30" FROM 
                                (SELECT F10003, ValStr, Ziua From Ptj_Intrari_2 WHERE '2019-06-01' <= CAST(Ziua AS date) AND CAST(Ziua AS date) <= '2019-06-30') AS source  
                                PIVOT  (MAX(ValStr) FOR Ziua IN (  [2019-06-01], [2019-06-02], [2019-06-03], [2019-06-04], [2019-06-05], [2019-06-06], [2019-06-07], [2019-06-08], [2019-06-09], [2019-06-10], [2019-06-11], [2019-06-12], [2019-06-13], [2019-06-14], [2019-06-15], [2019-06-16], [2019-06-17], [2019-06-18], [2019-06-19], [2019-06-20], [2019-06-21], [2019-06-22], [2019-06-23], [2019-06-24], [2019-06-25], [2019-06-26], [2019-06-27], [2019-06-28], [2019-06-29], [2019-06-30] )) pvt
                                ) pvt ON X.F10003=pvt.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=X.F10003 
                                LEFT JOIN (SELECT R.F10003, MIN(R.Ziua) AS ZiuaMin FROM Ptj_Intrari_2 R WHERE YEAR(R.Ziua)= 2019 AND MONTH(R.Ziua)= 6 GROUP BY R.F10003) Q ON Q.F10003=A.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Intrari_2 Y ON A.F10003=Y.F10003 AND Y.Ziua=Q.ZiuaMin
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_tblStariPontaj K ON K.Id = ISNULL(X.IdStare,1) 
                                LEFT JOIN Ptj_Contracte C on C.Id = Y.IdContract 
                                LEFT JOIN F089 DR ON DR.F08902 = A.F1009741 
                                 LEFT JOIN "viewCategoriePontaj" CTG ON A.F10003 = CTG.F10003 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma(X.F10003, '2019-06-30') dn 
                                OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, '2019-06-30') ddp 

							    LEFT JOIN F002 S2 ON Y.F10002 = S2.F00202
							    LEFT JOIN F003 S3 ON Y.F10004 = S3.F00304
							    LEFT JOIN F004 S4 ON Y.F10005 = S4.F00405

							    LEFT JOIN F005 H ON Y.F10006 = H.F00506
							    LEFT JOIN F006 I ON Y.F10007 = I.F00607

							    LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON Y.F100958 = S7.F00708
                                LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON Y.F100959 = S8.F00809

                                LEFT JOIN F062 L ON Y.F06204Default=L.F06204

                                LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                                WHERE X.An = 2019 AND X.Luna = 6 
                                ORDER BY AngajatNume) A
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2019 + 6 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE S.F10025 <> 900 AND CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2019-6-30' AND '2019-6-01' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003)

 where year(Ziua)=ent.An AND MONTH(Ziua)=ent.Luna AND Ptj_intrari.F10003=ent.F10003) 
                            FROM "Ptj_Cumulat" ent
                            WHERE  1=1  AND ent.F10003=9 AND 202007 <= (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") AND (ent."An" * 100 + ent."Luna") <= 202007;

END;

,CONVERT(datetime,DATEADD(minute, P."F58", '')) AS "FTmp58" ,CONVERT(datetime,DATEADD(minute, P."F59", '')) AS "FTmp59" ,
                            P.F10003 AS "Cheia",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Dept",
                            L."Denumire" AS "DescContract", M."Denumire" AS DescProgram, COALESCE(L."OreSup",1) AS "OreSup", COALESCE(L."Afisare",1) AS "Afisare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10022 <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <= A.F10023 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "F100Supervizori" FS WHERE FS.F10003=P.F10003 AND FS."IdSuper"=3 AND FS."IdUser"=2 AND CONVERT(date,FS."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,FS."DataSfarsit")) = 1
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Activ",  
                            COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) AS "IdStare", K."Culoare" AS "CuloareStare", K."Denumire" AS "NumeStare", 
                            CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" Z 
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON Z."IdAbsenta" = Y."Id"
                            WHERE Z.F10003 = P.F10003 AND Z."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= Z."DataSfarsit" AND Z."IdStare" = 3
                            AND Z."IdAbsenta" IN (SELECT "Id" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE "IdTipOre" = 1) AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj", 0) = 0) = 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "VineDinCereri", 
                            A.F10022, A.F10023,
                            (SELECT COALESCE(A."OreInVal",'') + ';'
                            FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b ON a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c ON a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."OreInVal" IS NOT NULL AND RTRIM(LTRIM(A."OreInVal")) <> '' AND B."IdContract"=P."IdContract" AND C."IdRol"=3 AND 
                            (((CASE WHEN(P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND P."ZiLibera" = 0) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.ZL,0) AND COALESCE(B.ZL,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.S,0) AND COALESCE(B.S,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.D,0) AND COALESCE(B.D,0) <> 0) OR
                            (COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = COALESCE(B.SL,0) AND COALESCE(B.SL,0) <> 0)) 
                            GROUP BY A."OreInVal"
                            ORDER BY A."OreInVal"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValActive",


							(SELECT COALESCE(A."Coloana",'') + ';'
                            FROM(
                            SELECT "Coloana" FROM "Ptj_tblAdmin" WHERE SUBSTRING("Coloana", 1, 3) = 'Val' AND "Coloana" NOT IN('ValAbs', 'ValStr') AND COALESCE("Blocat", 0) = 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" B ON A."IdGrup" = B."IdGrup"
                            WHERE B."IdUser" = 2 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            WHERE A."IdGrup" = -1 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            ) A
                            GROUP BY A."Coloana"
                            ORDER BY A."Coloana"
                            FOR XML PATH('')) AS "ValSecuritate",


	                        (select ',' + X."DenumireScurta" + '=' + X."Denumire" from ( 
                            select a."Id", b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id" as "IdAbsenta" , b.ZL as "ZileSapt", b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal", 0 AS "Tip" 
                            from "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            inner join "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b on a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            inner join "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c on a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."IdTipOre" = 1 
                            group by b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id", b.ZL, b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal"
                            ) x
                            WHERE COALESCE(X.DenumireScurta,'') <> '' AND X."IdContract" = P."IdContract" and X."IdRol" = 3 AND
                            ( (COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0)=(CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt"<6 AND P."ZiLibera"=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.S,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.S,0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.D,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.D,0) <> 0)
							OR (COALESCE(X.SL,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.SL,0) <> 0))
                            GROUP BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            ORDER BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValAbsente",

                            CASE WHEN (
                            CASE WHEN 3 = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 2 AND ((COALESCE(J."IdStare",1)=1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 2 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 4 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 6))) THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 1 AND(COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 4)) THEN 1 ELSE 0
                            END END END)=1 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*)
                            FROM "Ptj_relGrupSuper" BB
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupAngajat" CC ON BB."IdGrup"  = CC."IdGrup" 
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" DD ON CC.F10003 = DD.F10003 AND (-1 * BB."IdSuper")= DD."IdSuper"
                            WHERE DD.F10003=P.F10003 AND BB."IdRol"=3 AND DD."IdUser"=2
                            AND CONVERT(date,DD."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") 
                            AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,DD."DataSfarsit")) >= 1                            
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "DrepturiModif", 
                            Fct.F71804 AS "Functie", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", CA.F72404 AS "Categorie1", CB.F72404 AS "Categorie2",
                            CASE WHEN 
							    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON X."IdAbsenta"=Y."Id"
                                WHERE X."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= X."DataSfarsit" AND Y."DenumireScurta"=P."ValStr" AND
                                X.F10003=P.F10003 AND X."IdStare"=3 AND Y."IdTipOre"=1 AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj",0) != 1) = 0
                            THEN -55 ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN COALESCE("PoateSterge",0) = 0 THEN -33 ELSE COALESCE("TipMesaj",1) END FROM "Ptj_tblRoluri" WHERE "Id"=3) END AS "tblRoluri_PoateModifica",
                            ABSE."DenumireScurta" AS "ValAbs"                            
                            FROM "Ptj_Intrari" P
                            LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003 = P.F10003
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON P.F10002 = E.F00202
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON P.F10004 = F.F00304
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON P.F10005 = G.F00405
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON P.F10006 = H.F00506
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON P.F10007 = I.F00607
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Cumulat" J ON J.F10003=A.F10003 AND J."An"=YEAR(P."Ziua") AND J."Luna"=MONTH(P."Ziua")
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblStariPontaj" K ON COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = K."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Contracte" L ON P."IdContract"=L."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" M ON P."IdProgram"=M."Id"

                            LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON P.F100959 = S8.F00809
                            LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802

                            LEFT JOIN F724 CB ON A.F10062 = CB.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN (SELECT "DenumireScurta" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE COALESCE("DenumireScurta",'') <>'' GROUP BY "DenumireScurta") ABSE ON P."ValStr"=ABSE."DenumireScurta"

                            P.F10003 AS "Cheia",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Dept",
                            L."Denumire" AS "DescContract", M."Denumire" AS DescProgram, COALESCE(L."OreSup",1) AS "OreSup", COALESCE(L."Afisare",1) AS "Afisare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10022 <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <= A.F10023 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "F100Supervizori" FS WHERE FS.F10003=P.F10003 AND FS."IdSuper"=3 AND FS."IdUser"=2 AND CONVERT(date,FS."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,FS."DataSfarsit")) = 1
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Activ",  
                            COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) AS "IdStare", K."Culoare" AS "CuloareStare", K."Denumire" AS "NumeStare", 
                            CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" Z 
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON Z."IdAbsenta" = Y."Id"
                            WHERE Z.F10003 = P.F10003 AND Z."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= Z."DataSfarsit" AND Z."IdStare" = 3
                            AND Z."IdAbsenta" IN (SELECT "Id" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE "IdTipOre" = 1) AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj", 0) = 0) = 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "VineDinCereri", 
                            A.F10022, A.F10023,
                            (SELECT COALESCE(A."OreInVal",'') + ';'
                            FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b ON a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c ON a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."OreInVal" IS NOT NULL AND RTRIM(LTRIM(A."OreInVal")) <> '' AND B."IdContract"=P."IdContract" AND C."IdRol"=3 AND 
                            (((CASE WHEN(P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND P."ZiLibera" = 0) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.ZL,0) AND COALESCE(B.ZL,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.S,0) AND COALESCE(B.S,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.D,0) AND COALESCE(B.D,0) <> 0) OR
                            (COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = COALESCE(B.SL,0) AND COALESCE(B.SL,0) <> 0)) 
                            GROUP BY A."OreInVal"
                            ORDER BY A."OreInVal"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValActive",


							(SELECT COALESCE(A."Coloana",'') + ';'
                            FROM(
                            SELECT "Coloana" FROM "Ptj_tblAdmin" WHERE SUBSTRING("Coloana", 1, 3) = 'Val' AND "Coloana" NOT IN('ValAbs', 'ValStr') AND COALESCE("Blocat", 0) = 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" B ON A."IdGrup" = B."IdGrup"
                            WHERE B."IdUser" = 2 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            WHERE A."IdGrup" = -1 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            ) A
                            GROUP BY A."Coloana"
                            ORDER BY A."Coloana"
                            FOR XML PATH('')) AS "ValSecuritate",


	                        (select ',' + X."DenumireScurta" + '=' + X."Denumire" from ( 
                            select a."Id", b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id" as "IdAbsenta" , b.ZL as "ZileSapt", b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal", 0 AS "Tip" 
                            from "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            inner join "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b on a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            inner join "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c on a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."IdTipOre" = 1 
                            group by b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id", b.ZL, b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal"
                            ) x
                            WHERE COALESCE(X.DenumireScurta,'') <> '' AND X."IdContract" = P."IdContract" and X."IdRol" = 3 AND
                            ( (COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0)=(CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt"<6 AND P."ZiLibera"=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.S,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.S,0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.D,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.D,0) <> 0)
							OR (COALESCE(X.SL,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.SL,0) <> 0))
                            GROUP BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            ORDER BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValAbsente",

                            CASE WHEN (
                            CASE WHEN 3 = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 2 AND ((COALESCE(J."IdStare",1)=1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 2 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 4 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 6))) THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 1 AND(COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 4)) THEN 1 ELSE 0
                            END END END)=1 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*)
                            FROM "Ptj_relGrupSuper" BB
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupAngajat" CC ON BB."IdGrup"  = CC."IdGrup" 
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" DD ON CC.F10003 = DD.F10003 AND (-1 * BB."IdSuper")= DD."IdSuper"
                            WHERE DD.F10003=P.F10003 AND BB."IdRol"=3 AND DD."IdUser"=2
                            AND CONVERT(date,DD."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") 
                            AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,DD."DataSfarsit")) >= 1                            
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "DrepturiModif", 
                            Fct.F71804 AS "Functie", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", CA.F72404 AS "Categorie1", CB.F72404 AS "Categorie2",
                            CASE WHEN 
							    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON X."IdAbsenta"=Y."Id"
                                WHERE X."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= X."DataSfarsit" AND Y."DenumireScurta"=P."ValStr" AND
                                X.F10003=P.F10003 AND X."IdStare"=3 AND Y."IdTipOre"=1 AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj",0) != 1) = 0
                            THEN -55 ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN COALESCE("PoateSterge",0) = 0 THEN -33 ELSE COALESCE("TipMesaj",1) END FROM "Ptj_tblRoluri" WHERE "Id"=3) END AS "tblRoluri_PoateModifica",
                            ABSE."DenumireScurta" AS "ValAbs"                            
                            FROM "Ptj_Intrari" P
                            LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003 = P.F10003
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON P.F10002 = E.F00202
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON P.F10004 = F.F00304
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON P.F10005 = G.F00405
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON P.F10006 = H.F00506
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON P.F10007 = I.F00607
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Cumulat" J ON J.F10003=A.F10003 AND J."An"=YEAR(P."Ziua") AND J."Luna"=MONTH(P."Ziua")
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblStariPontaj" K ON COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = K."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Contracte" L ON P."IdContract"=L."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" M ON P."IdProgram"=M."Id"

                            LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON P.F100958 = S7.F00708
                            LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON P.F100959 = S8.F00809
                            LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CA ON A.F10061 = CA.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CB ON A.F10062 = CB.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN (SELECT "DenumireScurta" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE COALESCE("DenumireScurta",'') <>'' GROUP BY "DenumireScurta") ABSE ON P."ValStr"=ABSE."DenumireScurta"
                            
                            WHERE CAST(P."Ziua" AS DATE) <= A.F10023
                             AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") = '2020-07-27' AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2020 + 7 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE S.F10025 <> 900 AND CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2020-7-27' AND '2020-7-27' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003) ORDER BY A.F10003, CONVERT(date,P."Ziua")

                            P.F10003 AS "Cheia",
                            E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Dept",
                            L."Denumire" AS "DescContract", M."Denumire" AS DescProgram, COALESCE(L."OreSup",1) AS "OreSup", COALESCE(L."Afisare",1) AS "Afisare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10022 <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <= A.F10023 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "F100Supervizori" FS WHERE FS.F10003=P.F10003 AND FS."IdSuper"=3 AND FS."IdUser"=2 AND CONVERT(date,FS."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,FS."DataSfarsit")) = 1
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Activ",  
                            COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) AS "IdStare", K."Culoare" AS "CuloareStare", K."Denumire" AS "NumeStare", 
                            CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" Z 
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON Z."IdAbsenta" = Y."Id"
                            WHERE Z.F10003 = P.F10003 AND Z."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= Z."DataSfarsit" AND Z."IdStare" = 3
                            AND Z."IdAbsenta" IN (SELECT "Id" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE "IdTipOre" = 1) AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj", 0) = 0) = 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "VineDinCereri", 
                            A.F10022, A.F10023,
                            (SELECT COALESCE(A."OreInVal",'') + ';'
                            FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b ON a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c ON a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."OreInVal" IS NOT NULL AND RTRIM(LTRIM(A."OreInVal")) <> '' AND B."IdContract"=P."IdContract" AND C."IdRol"=3 AND 
                            (((CASE WHEN(P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND P."ZiLibera" = 0) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.ZL,0) AND COALESCE(B.ZL,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.S,0) AND COALESCE(B.S,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.D,0) AND COALESCE(B.D,0) <> 0) OR
                            (COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = COALESCE(B.SL,0) AND COALESCE(B.SL,0) <> 0)) 
                            GROUP BY A."OreInVal"
                            ORDER BY A."OreInVal"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValActive",


							(SELECT COALESCE(A."Coloana",'') + ';'
                            FROM(
                            SELECT "Coloana" FROM "Ptj_tblAdmin" WHERE SUBSTRING("Coloana", 1, 3) = 'Val' AND "Coloana" NOT IN('ValAbs', 'ValStr') AND COALESCE("Blocat", 0) = 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" B ON A."IdGrup" = B."IdGrup"
                            WHERE B."IdUser" = 2 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            WHERE A."IdGrup" = -1 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            ) A
                            GROUP BY A."Coloana"
                            ORDER BY A."Coloana"
                            FOR XML PATH('')) AS "ValSecuritate",


	                        (select ',' + X."DenumireScurta" + '=' + X."Denumire" from ( 
                            select a."Id", b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id" as "IdAbsenta" , b.ZL as "ZileSapt", b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal", 0 AS "Tip" 
                            from "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            inner join "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b on a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            inner join "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c on a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."IdTipOre" = 1 
                            group by b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id", b.ZL, b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal"
                            ) x
                            WHERE COALESCE(X.DenumireScurta,'') <> '' AND X."IdContract" = P."IdContract" and X."IdRol" = 3 AND
                            ( (COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0)=(CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt"<6 AND P."ZiLibera"=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.S,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.S,0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.D,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.D,0) <> 0)
							OR (COALESCE(X.SL,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.SL,0) <> 0))
                            GROUP BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            ORDER BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValAbsente",

                            CASE WHEN (
                            CASE WHEN 3 = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 2 AND ((COALESCE(J."IdStare",1)=1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 2 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 4 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 6))) THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 1 AND(COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 4)) THEN 1 ELSE 0
                            END END END)=1 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*)
                            FROM "Ptj_relGrupSuper" BB
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupAngajat" CC ON BB."IdGrup"  = CC."IdGrup" 
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" DD ON CC.F10003 = DD.F10003 AND (-1 * BB."IdSuper")= DD."IdSuper"
                            WHERE DD.F10003=P.F10003 AND BB."IdRol"=3 AND DD."IdUser"=2
                            AND CONVERT(date,DD."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") 
                            AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,DD."DataSfarsit")) >= 1                            
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "DrepturiModif", 
                            Fct.F71804 AS "Functie", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", CA.F72404 AS "Categorie1", CB.F72404 AS "Categorie2",
                            CASE WHEN 
							    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON X."IdAbsenta"=Y."Id"
                                WHERE X."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= X."DataSfarsit" AND Y."DenumireScurta"=P."ValStr" AND
                                X.F10003=P.F10003 AND X."IdStare"=3 AND Y."IdTipOre"=1 AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj",0) != 1) = 0
                            THEN -55 ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN COALESCE("PoateSterge",0) = 0 THEN -33 ELSE COALESCE("TipMesaj",1) END FROM "Ptj_tblRoluri" WHERE "Id"=3) END AS "tblRoluri_PoateModifica",
                            ABSE."DenumireScurta" AS "ValAbs"                            
                            FROM "Ptj_Intrari" P
                            LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003 = P.F10003
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON P.F10002 = E.F00202
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON P.F10004 = F.F00304
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON P.F10005 = G.F00405
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON P.F10006 = H.F00506
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON P.F10007 = I.F00607
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Cumulat" J ON J.F10003=A.F10003 AND J."An"=YEAR(P."Ziua") AND J."Luna"=MONTH(P."Ziua")
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblStariPontaj" K ON COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = K."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Contracte" L ON P."IdContract"=L."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" M ON P."IdProgram"=M."Id"

                            LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON P.F100958 = S7.F00708
                            LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON P.F100959 = S8.F00809
                            LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CA ON A.F10061 = CA.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CB ON A.F10062 = CB.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN (SELECT "DenumireScurta" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE COALESCE("DenumireScurta",'') <>'' GROUP BY "DenumireScurta") ABSE ON P."ValStr"=ABSE."DenumireScurta"
                            
                            WHERE CAST(P."Ziua" AS DATE) <= A.F10023
                             AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") = '2020-07-25' AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2020 + 7 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE S.F10025 <> 900 AND CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2020-7-25' AND '2020-7-25' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003) ORDER BY A.F10003, CONVERT(date,P."Ziua")

                            ( (COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0)=(CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt"<6 AND P."ZiLibera"=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.S,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.S,0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.D,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.D,0) <> 0)
							OR (COALESCE(X.SL,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.SL,0) <> 0))
                            GROUP BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            ORDER BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValAbsente",

                            CASE WHEN (
                            CASE WHEN 3 = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 2 AND ((COALESCE(J."IdStare",1)=1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 2 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 4 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 6))) THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 1 AND(COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 4)) THEN 1 ELSE 0
                            END END END)=1 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*)
                            FROM "Ptj_relGrupSuper" BB
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupAngajat" CC ON BB."IdGrup"  = CC."IdGrup" 
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" DD ON CC.F10003 = DD.F10003 AND (-1 * BB."IdSuper")= DD."IdSuper"
                            WHERE DD.F10003=P.F10003 AND BB."IdRol"=3 AND DD."IdUser"=2
                            AND CONVERT(date,DD."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") 
                            AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,DD."DataSfarsit")) >= 1                            
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "DrepturiModif", 
                            Fct.F71804 AS "Functie", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", CA.F72404 AS "Categorie1", CB.F72404 AS "Categorie2",
                            CASE WHEN 
							    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON X."IdAbsenta"=Y."Id"
                                WHERE X."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= X."DataSfarsit" AND Y."DenumireScurta"=P."ValStr" AND
                                X.F10003=P.F10003 AND X."IdStare"=3 AND Y."IdTipOre"=1 AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj",0) != 1) = 0
                            THEN -55 ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN COALESCE("PoateSterge",0) = 0 THEN -33 ELSE COALESCE("TipMesaj",1) END FROM "Ptj_tblRoluri" WHERE "Id"=3) END AS "tblRoluri_PoateModifica",
                            ABSE."DenumireScurta" AS "ValAbs"                            
                            FROM "Ptj_Intrari" P
                            LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003 = P.F10003
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON P.F10002 = E.F00202
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON P.F10004 = F.F00304
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON P.F10005 = G.F00405
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON P.F10006 = H.F00506
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON P.F10007 = I.F00607
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Cumulat" J ON J.F10003=A.F10003 AND J."An"=YEAR(P."Ziua") AND J."Luna"=MONTH(P."Ziua")
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblStariPontaj" K ON COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = K."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Contracte" L ON P."IdContract"=L."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" M ON P."IdProgram"=M."Id"

                            LEFT JOIN F007 S7 ON P.F100958 = S7.F00708
                            LEFT JOIN F008 S8 ON P.F100959 = S8.F00809
                            LEFT JOIN F718 Fct ON A.F10071=Fct.F71802
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CA ON A.F10061 = CA.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN F724 CB ON A.F10062 = CB.F72402
                            LEFT JOIN (SELECT "DenumireScurta" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE COALESCE("DenumireScurta",'') <>'' GROUP BY "DenumireScurta") ABSE ON P."ValStr"=ABSE."DenumireScurta"
                            
                            WHERE CAST(P."Ziua" AS DATE) <= A.F10023
                             AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") = '2020-07-24' AND A.F10003 IN ( SELECT X.F10003 FROM (  SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup WHERE C.IdSuper =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.f10003 UNION SELECT B.f10003 FROM relGrupAngajat B INNER JOIN Ptj_relGrupSuper C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup INNER JOIN F100Supervizori D ON D.F10003 = B.F10003 AND D.IdSuper = (-1 * C.IdSuper) AND (100 * 2020 + 7 BETWEEN isnull(100 * year(D.DataInceput) + MONTH(D.DataInceput), 190000) AND isnull(100 * year(D.DataSfarsit) + MONTH(D.DataSfarsit), 210000))  WHERE D.IdUser =2 AND C.IdRol=3 GROUP BY B.F10003) X  WHERE X.F10003 IN (SELECT S.F10003 FROM F100 S WHERE S.F10025 <> 900 AND CONVERT(date,S.F10022) <> CONVERT(date,S.F100993)  AND F10022 <= '2020-7-24' AND '2020-7-24' <= F100993 ) GROUP BY X.F10003) ORDER BY A.F10003, CONVERT(date,P."Ziua")

                            E.F00204 AS "Companie", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie", G.F00406 AS "Filiala", H.F00507 AS "Sectie", I.F00608 AS "Dept",
                            L."Denumire" AS "DescContract", M."Denumire" AS DescProgram, COALESCE(L."OreSup",1) AS "OreSup", COALESCE(L."Afisare",1) AS "Afisare",
                            CASE WHEN A.F10022 <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <= A.F10023 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "F100Supervizori" FS WHERE FS.F10003=P.F10003 AND FS."IdSuper"=3 AND FS."IdUser"=2 AND CONVERT(date,FS."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,FS."DataSfarsit")) = 1
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "Activ",  
                            COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) AS "IdStare", K."Culoare" AS "CuloareStare", K."Denumire" AS "NumeStare", 
                            CASE WHEN (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" Z 
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON Z."IdAbsenta" = Y."Id"
                            WHERE Z.F10003 = P.F10003 AND Z."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= Z."DataSfarsit" AND Z."IdStare" = 3
                            AND Z."IdAbsenta" IN (SELECT "Id" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" WHERE "IdTipOre" = 1) AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj", 0) = 0) = 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS "VineDinCereri", 
                            A.F10022, A.F10023,
                            (SELECT COALESCE(A."OreInVal",'') + ';'
                            FROM "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b ON a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            INNER JOIN "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c ON a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."OreInVal" IS NOT NULL AND RTRIM(LTRIM(A."OreInVal")) <> '' AND B."IdContract"=P."IdContract" AND C."IdRol"=3 AND 
                            (((CASE WHEN(P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND P."ZiLibera" = 0) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.ZL,0) AND COALESCE(B.ZL,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.S,0) AND COALESCE(B.S,0) <> 0) OR
                            ((CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COALESCE(B.D,0) AND COALESCE(B.D,0) <> 0) OR
                            (COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = COALESCE(B.SL,0) AND COALESCE(B.SL,0) <> 0)) 
                            GROUP BY A."OreInVal"
                            ORDER BY A."OreInVal"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValActive",


							(SELECT COALESCE(A."Coloana",'') + ';'
                            FROM(
                            SELECT "Coloana" FROM "Ptj_tblAdmin" WHERE SUBSTRING("Coloana", 1, 3) = 'Val' AND "Coloana" NOT IN('ValAbs', 'ValStr') AND COALESCE("Blocat", 0) = 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" B ON A."IdGrup" = B."IdGrup"
                            WHERE B."IdUser" = 2 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            UNION
                            SELECT REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            FROM "Securitate" A
                            WHERE A."IdGrup" = -1 AND A."IdForm" = 'pontaj.pontajdetaliat' AND SUBSTRING(A."IdColoana", 1, 6) = 'ValTmp'
                            GROUP BY REPLACE(A."IdColoana", 'Tmp', '')
                            HAVING MIN(COALESCE(A."Blocat",0))= 1
                            ) A
                            GROUP BY A."Coloana"
                            ORDER BY A."Coloana"
                            FOR XML PATH('')) AS "ValSecuritate",


	                        (select ',' + X."DenumireScurta" + '=' + X."Denumire" from ( 
                            select a."Id", b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id" as "IdAbsenta" , b.ZL as "ZileSapt", b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal", 0 AS "Tip" 
                            from "Ptj_tblAbsente" a
                            inner join "Ptj_ContracteAbsente" b on a."Id" = b."IdAbsenta"
                            inner join "Ptj_relRolAbsenta" c on a."Id" = c."IdAbsenta"
                            WHERE A."IdTipOre" = 1 
                            group by b."IdContract", c."IdRol", a."Id", b.ZL, b.S, b.D, b.SL, a."Denumire", a."DenumireScurta", c."IdAbsentePermise", A."OreInVal"
                            ) x
                            WHERE COALESCE(X.DenumireScurta,'') <> '' AND X."IdContract" = P."IdContract" and X."IdRol" = 3 AND
                            ( (COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0)=(CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt"<6 AND P."ZiLibera"=0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X."ZileSapt",0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.S,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 6 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.S,0) <> 0)
                            OR (COALESCE(X.D,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.D,0) <> 0)
							OR (COALESCE(X.SL,0) = (CASE WHEN P."ZiSapt" < 6 AND COALESCE(P."ZiLiberaLegala",0) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AND COALESCE(X.SL,0) <> 0))
                            GROUP BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            ORDER BY X."Id", X."DenumireScurta", X."Denumire"
                            FOR XML PATH ('')) AS "ValAbsente",

                            CASE WHEN 3 = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 2 AND ((COALESCE(J."IdStare",1)=1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 2 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 4 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = 6))) THEN 1 ELSE 
                            CASE WHEN (3 = 1 AND(COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 1 OR COALESCE(J."IdStare", 1) = 4)) THEN 1 ELSE 0
                            END END END)=1 AND
                            (SELECT COUNT(*)
                            FROM "Ptj_relGrupSuper" BB
                            INNER JOIN "relGrupAngajat" CC ON BB."IdGrup"  = CC."IdGrup" 
                            INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" DD ON CC.F10003 = DD.F10003 AND (-1 * BB."IdSuper")= DD."IdSuper"
                            WHERE DD.F10003=P.F10003 AND BB."IdRol"=3 AND DD."IdUser"=2
                            AND CONVERT(date,DD."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") 
                            AND CONVERT(date,P."Ziua") <=  CONVERT(date,DD."DataSfarsit")) >= 1                            
                            THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS "DrepturiModif", 
                            Fct.F71804 AS "Functie", S7.F00709 AS "Subdept", S8.F00810 AS "Birou", CA.F72404 AS "Categorie1", CB.F72404 AS "Categorie2",
                            CASE WHEN 
							    (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Y ON X."IdAbsenta"=Y."Id"
                                WHERE X."DataInceput" <= P."Ziua" AND P."Ziua" <= X."DataSfarsit" AND Y."DenumireScurta"=P."ValStr" AND
                                X.F10003=P.F10003 AND X."IdStare"=3 AND Y."IdTipOre"=1 AND COALESCE(Y."NuTrimiteInPontaj",0) != 1) = 0
                            THEN -55 ELSE (SELECT CASE WHEN COALESCE("PoateSterge",0) = 0 THEN -33 ELSE COALESCE("TipMesaj",1) END FROM "Ptj_tblRoluri" WHERE "Id"=3) END AS "tblRoluri_PoateModifica",
                            ABSE."DenumireScurta" AS "ValAbs"                            
                            FROM "Ptj_Intrari" P
                            LEFT JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003 = P.F10003
                            LEFT JOIN F002 E ON P.F10002 = E.F00202
                            LEFT JOIN F003 F ON P.F10004 = F.F00304
                            LEFT JOIN F004 G ON P.F10005 = G.F00405
                            LEFT JOIN F005 H ON P.F10006 = H.F00506
                            LEFT JOIN F006 I ON P.F10007 = I.F00607
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Cumulat" J ON J.F10003=A.F10003 AND J."An"=YEAR(P."Ziua") AND J."Luna"=MONTH(P."Ziua")
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblStariPontaj" K ON COALESCE(J."IdStare",1) = K."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Contracte" L ON P."IdContract"=L."Id"
                            LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" M ON P."IdProgram"=M."Id"
